1. BASIC PURPOSE OF THE POSITION:
Support in ensuring the compliance of PVM’s products (chewing gum, candies, snacks made with dried fruit and nuts) with laws and technical standards applicable to Food Industry as well as Group’s policies.

Territory involved: Vietnam. Further regulatory activities are also related to export markets such as for instance EU, MENA, EFE, etc.
Main regulatory topics: food and labelling, advertisement, toys, contest with prizes.
Requirements for the role: accuracy, flexibility, quick learner, very good communication skills (written and spoken), analytical skill, big picture thinking, high level of knowledge on food law, vitamins, minerals, claims (health and nutrition) and technical aspects. Experience in working with associations and authority.

MAIN AREAS OF RESPONSIBILITY (TO BE MANAGED WITH THE TEAM):
1. Monitor (e.g. through authority website, consultants, associations, etc.) and study food and labeling legislation (e.g. additives, ingredients, health and nutrition claims, novel foods, contaminants, labelling rules, etc) and their possible revisions and any other regulation related to topics under the responsibility of Regulatory (e.g. adv, sustainability, toys, etc.) for the local market;
2. Impact assessment of legislation under regulatory responsibility on the Company and Company’s products;
3. Share information and communication on legislation under the regulatory responsibility with other functions within the organization;
4. Support in providing updates on regulatory topics of interest;
5. Work closely with Marketing providing advice on project feasibility and compliance (concept, food category, pictorials, health and nutrition claims, marketing claims, new ingredients, risk assessment, etc);
6. Support R&D providing advice on recipe compliance and other matters (e.g. additives, raw materials, ingredients, nutrition information, etc);
7. Prepare and issue ingredient lists and nutrition information upon recipe shared by R&D;
8. Check the product labels providing the final approval according to local regulations to ensure the compliance;
9. Support GRD, Group Marketing and Group Regulatory on projects and critical matters (projects, law interpretation, ingredients, etc) of interest providing information and advice;
10. Support in verifying the advertisement and promotional material and prepare advice in coordination with Group Regulatory;
11. Toys & Gadgets: manage product and label compliance for domestic projects (i.e. advice on project feasibility, contact with external Lab, coordination with Group Regulatory and other functions, technical standards and legislation , etc.)
12. Contest with prizes: knowledge of applicable legislation, compliance of communication and info displayed on the labels, terms and conditions mandatory info)
13. Export countries: verify product ingredients and additives compliance, coordinate the information sharing with other functions, GRA and local regulatory in other countries, support in the preparation of IL/NI.

1. Công tác đánh giá nội bộ
• Lập kế hoạch đánh giá nội bộ hàng năm/định kỳ theo các hệ thống quản lý áp dụng (ISO 9001, ISO 14001, IATF 16949…);
• Thực hiện đánh giá nội bộ tại các phòng ban/bộ phận theo kế hoạch đã phê duyệt;
